                <li>Preparing for and taking the SAT, ACT, & SAT Subject Tests</li>
                <li>Choosing & continuing with appropriate extracurricular activities</li>
                <li>“Do What You Are” personality assessment</li>
                <li>Financial Aid: How to determine if a family will qualify & what is needed to apply</li>
            </div>
            <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-lg-1-2">
                <li>Developing a list of possible colleges, noting application requirements & deadlines</li>
                <li>Approaching teachers & counselors for letters of recommendation</li>
                <li>Choosing the most appropriate prompt for the application essay and writing one draft</li>
                <li>Preparing for college visits</li>
                <li>Considering summer plans: internships, part-time jobs, & pre-college programs</li>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <hr class="section-divider"/>
