        <h3 class="pure-u-1">High School Seniors</h3>
        <div class="package-copy pure-g">
            <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-lg-1-2">
                <li>Review of student and parent questionnaires & transcript</li>
                <li>Narrowing your college list to your final choices, with a combination of safety, target and reach schools</li>
                <li>Confirming all application deadlines & application components for your final choices</li>
                <li>Approaching teachers, mentors, & counselors for letters of recommendation</li>
                <li>Polishing your personal essay & supplemental essay questions</li>
            </div>
            <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-lg-1-2">
                <li>Completing and submitting your college applications</li>
                <li>Financial Aid: How to determine if a family will qualify & what is needed to apply</li>
